title: Happy 40th Birthday Randy Moss...The Punt Returner?!?! | Vikings Blog | KFAN FM 100.3
text:
Happy 40th Birthday Randy Moss...The Punt Returner?!?! posted by Alexander Shun - share 
Today is the day that former Minnesota Vikings wide receiver Randy Moss turns 40. 
Such a day is one to celebrate the incredible and amazing accomplishments of one of the most prolific receivers the NFL has ever seen. 
Everyone and their mother remembers Randy Moss the wide receiver, but how many remember Randy Moss the punt returner? 
For the big 4-0 birthday, I present to you the time that Moss returned a punt 64 yards against the Kansas City Chiefs to tie the game late in the fourth quarter. 
Enjoy!
